<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Plataforma Migrada</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:       #07080f;
      --surface:  #0e0f1a;
      --card:     #11121f;
      --border:   #1c1d30;
      --accent:   #7c6fff;
      --accent2:  #b49dff;
      --danger:   #ff6b6b;
      --text:     #ddddf0;
      --muted:    #52536a;
      --subtle:   #1a1b2e;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,111,255,0.18) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 36px 36px;
      pointer-events: none;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, black 40%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .glow {
      position: fixed;
      width: 700px; height: 700px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,111,255,0.10) 0%, transparent 65%);
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: breathe 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes breathe {
      0%,100% { opacity:.7; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1);   }
      50%      { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.08);}
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 1px rgba(124,111,255,0.06),
        0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      animation: riseIn .9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) both;
    }
    @keyframes riseIn {
      from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(36px) scale(.98); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform: none; }
    }

    .illustration {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0c0d1e 0%, #0f0f1f 60%, #12102a 100%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 56px 40px 48px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .illustration::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        transparent, transparent 28px,
        rgba(124,111,255,0.04) 28px, rgba(124,111,255,0.04) 29px
      );
    }
    .illustration svg {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(340px, 90%);
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 40px rgba(124,111,255,0.18));
    }

    .srv-group { animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes float {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0);   }
      50%      { transform: translateY(-6px); }
    }

    .status-dot { animation: blink 1.6s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes blink {
      0%,100% { opacity: 1; }
      50%      { opacity: .15; }
    }

    .arrow-path {
      stroke-dasharray: 120;
      stroke-dashoffset: 120;
      animation: drawArrow 1.4s .5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;
    }
    @keyframes drawArrow { to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; } }

    .body { padding: 48px 56px 52px; }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--danger);
      background: rgba(255,107,107,.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,107,.2);
      padding: 5px 13px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .badge-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--danger);
      animation: blink 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 44px);
      line-height: 1.22;
      letter-spacing: -.025em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 em {
      font-style: normal;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .desc {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 480px;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .hr {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .contacts {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .contacts .full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: var(--subtle);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s, transform .15s;
    }
    .contact-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(124,111,255,.45);
      background: rgba(124,111,255,.07);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .ci-icon {
      width: 38px; height: 38px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(124,111,255,.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(124,111,255,.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ci-icon svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; color: var(--accent2); }

    .ci-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
    .ci-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .ci-value {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .note {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .note svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: .45; }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .body { padding: 36px 28px 40px; }
      .contacts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .contacts .full { grid-column: auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glow"></div>

  <div class="card">

    <!-- ILLUSTRATION -->
    <div class="illustration">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 340 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <radialGradient id="bgGlow" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
            <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#7c6fff" stop-opacity=".15"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7c6fff" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>
          <linearGradient id="arrowGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
            <stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#ff6b6b"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#b49dff"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <style>
            @keyframes fadeIn { from{opacity:0} to{opacity:1} }
          </style>
        </defs>

        <ellipse cx="170" cy="105" rx="130" ry="70" fill="url(#bgGlow)" opacity=".5"/>

        <!-- OLD SERVER -->
        <g class="srv-group" style="animation-delay:.3s">
          <rect x="28" y="60" width="80" height="100" rx="10" fill="#0e0f1e" stroke="#2a2b40" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <rect x="38" y="73" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#14152a" stroke="#222340" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="38" y="92" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#14152a" stroke="#222340" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="38" y="111" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#14152a" stroke="#222340" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="88" cy="79.5" r="3.5" fill="#ff6b6b" class="status-dot"/>
          <circle cx="88" cy="98.5" r="3.5" fill="#ff6b6b" class="status-dot" style="animation-delay:.4s"/>
          <circle cx="88" cy="117.5" r="3.5" fill="#3a3b55"/>
          <circle cx="68" cy="95" r="30" fill="rgba(255,107,107,0.06)" stroke="rgba(255,107,107,0.18)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          <line x1="54" y1="81" x2="82" y2="109" stroke="#ff6b6b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".7"/>
          <line x1="82" y1="81" x2="54" y2="109" stroke="#ff6b6b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".7"/>
          <text x="68" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#52536a" letter-spacing=".08em">DOMINIO ANTERIOR</text>
        </g>

        <!-- ARROW -->
        <path class="arrow-path" d="M118 100 Q170 80 222 100"
          stroke="url(#arrowGrad)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="6 4" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M216 94 L224 100 L216 106" stroke="#b49dff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
          style="opacity:0; animation: fadeIn .3s 1.8s forwards"/>
        <text x="170" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif" font-size="8.5" fill="#7c6fff" letter-spacing=".06em"
          style="opacity:0; animation: fadeIn .4s 1.4s forwards">MIGRADO</text>

        <!-- NEW SERVER -->
        <g class="srv-group">
          <rect x="232" y="60" width="80" height="100" rx="10" fill="#0e0f1e" stroke="rgba(124,111,255,.5)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <rect x="242" y="73" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#13142a" stroke="rgba(124,111,255,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="242" y="92" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#13142a" stroke="rgba(124,111,255,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="242" y="111" width="60" height="13" rx="4" fill="#13142a" stroke="rgba(124,111,255,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="292" cy="79.5" r="3.5" fill="#6cffb8" class="status-dot"/>
          <circle cx="292" cy="98.5" r="3.5" fill="#6cffb8" class="status-dot" style="animation-delay:.5s"/>
          <circle cx="292" cy="117.5" r="3.5" fill="#6cffb8" class="status-dot" style="animation-delay:1s"/>
          <circle cx="272" cy="95" r="30" fill="rgba(124,111,255,0.06)" stroke="rgba(124,111,255,0.3)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          <path d="M260 96 L268 104 L284 86" stroke="#b49dff" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <text x="272" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#7c6fff" letter-spacing=".08em">NUEVA PLATAFORMA</text>
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- BODY -->
    <div class="body">

      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        Aviso de migración
      </div>

      <h1>
       <em> Hemos migrado nuestra plataforma</em>
      </h1>

      <p class="desc">
        Este dominio ya no se encuentra activo. Hemos trasladado todos nuestros
        servicios a una nueva dirección. Si necesitas acceso o tienes alguna
        pregunta, por favor contáctanos, estamos disponibles para ayudarte.
      </p>

      <div class="hr"></div>
      <p class="section-label">Ponte en contacto con nosotros para mayor información</p>

      <p class="note">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/>
        </svg>
        Disculpa los inconvenientes. Nuestro equipo está disponible para guiarte en la transición.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>